Deceptive Trade
01 Nov 2019, 17:23 by BRIEF
AUSTIN, Texas — Texas accuses Vickery-Young & Associates, Jamie W. Vickery, Amber Vickery, et al., all of Kentucky, of deceptive trade and abusive telemarketing, in Travis County Court.
